Class Production

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.hiof.olawp.oblig5.model.Production
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Episode, Film

    public abstract class Production
extends java.lang.Object
    Production is a class representing a production, in this case a film or a TvShow Holds information like title, runtime, description, relasedate, director and a list of roles
